description: Welcome to the Award Winning Sweet Auburn BBQ -Health Food For The Soul!Has a hot desire for BBQ taken hold of you? If you haven’t tried Sweet Auburn BBQ in downtown Atlanta, then you’re in for a treat. This is Southern barbecue with a twist - the melding of French refinement, Asian spice and Mexican flair that only the unique minds of Sweet Auburn can offer. With a wide selection and BBQ know-how as big as the great state of Georgia, this place has the goods to make your mouth water and your taste-buds sing.Try wonders such as amazing slow smoked ribs; tender, succulent, meaty brisket; mac & cheese, the mother of all comfort food; and much, much more!Don't miss this truly fantastic truck!
name: Sweet Auburn BBQ
